[
  {
    "text": "- So many niece and\nnephew asking Uncle Roger",
    "start": 0.15,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "to review Nick DiGiovanni making ramen.",
    "start": 3.27,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ramen. I've been wanting\nto make this forever,",
    "start": 6.47,
    "duration": 2.59
  },
  {
    "text": "but now is the time.",
    "start": 9.06,
    "duration": 1.01
  },
  {
    "text": "- This guy Harvard graduate,",
    "start": 10.07,
    "duration": 1.83
  },
  {
    "text": "Master Chef finalist,",
    "start": 11.9,
    "duration": 1.53
  },
  {
    "text": "and have the smoothest\nbaby face out there.",
    "start": 13.43,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Fuiyoh!",
    "start": 16.25,
    "duration": 1.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see how he do.",
    "start": 17.62,
    "duration": 1.203
  },
  {
    "text": "Before we start,",
    "start": 19.92,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "my nephew Nigel",
    "start": 21.02,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "trying out new character on his podcast.",
    "start": 22.27,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "He is Uncle Roger long\nlost Italian cousin.",
    "start": 25.35,
    "duration": 3.64
  },
  {
    "text": "- No, no!",
    "start": 28.99,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Zio Ruggero!",
    "start": 29.823,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Why?",
    "start": 30.656,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Because people be (beep) up carbonara!",
    "start": 31.489,
    "duration": 2.563
  },
  {
    "text": "No no no!",
    "start": 34.052,
    "duration": 1.738
  },
  {
    "text": "No cream in carbonara!",
    "start": 35.79,
    "duration": 1.352
  },
  {
    "text": "Mamma mia!",
    "start": 37.142,
    "duration": 1.911
  },
  {
    "text": "Link in description.",
    "start": 39.053,
    "duration": 1.317
  },
  {
    "text": "Give the clip a like.",
    "start": 40.37,
    "duration": 1.33
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe he will review bad\nBBC Food carbonara video.",
    "start": 41.7,
    "duration": 4.82
  },
  {
    "text": "- I know so many of you\nhave asked for ramen",
    "start": 46.52,
    "duration": 2.03
  },
  {
    "text": "for so, so long.",
    "start": 48.55,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "So today we're making tonkatsu ramen.",
    "start": 49.67,
    "duration": 2.253
  },
  {
    "text": "- What he say? What he say?",
    "start": 52.99,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "- So today we're making tonkatsu ramen.",
    "start": 55.0,
    "duration": 2.251
  },
  {
    "text": "- Tonkatsu...",
    "start": 57.251,
    "duration": 1.619
  },
  {
    "text": "Nephew Nick, I think you mean tonkotsu.",
    "start": 58.87,
    "duration": 2.95
  },
  {
    "text": "In Japanese,",
    "start": 61.82,
    "duration": 1.01
  },
  {
    "text": "ton mean pork.",
    "start": 62.83,
    "duration": 1.39
  },
  {
    "text": "Kotsu mean bone.",
    "start": 64.22,
    "duration": 1.31
  },
  {
    "text": "So tonkotsu ramen makes sense.",
    "start": 65.53,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "It pork bone ramen, but katsu mean cutlet.",
    "start": 67.77,
    "duration": 4.02
  },
  {
    "text": "So tonkatsu mean fried piece of pork.",
    "start": 71.79,
    "duration": 3.77
  },
  {
    "text": "That completely different thing.",
    "start": 75.56,
    "duration": 1.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Say it properly.",
    "start": 77.55,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "Tonkotsu, tonkotsu.",
    "start": 78.84,
    "duration": 1.287
  },
  {
    "text": "- I've already started a couple of things.",
    "start": 81.62,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "So for now let's pop back to yesterday,",
    "start": 82.97,
    "duration": 2.27
  },
  {
    "text": "when I hadn't shaved yet,",
    "start": 85.24,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "and we'll go to an Asian market.",
    "start": 86.41,
    "duration": 1.49
  },
  {
    "text": "So we've just pulled up to this -",
    "start": 87.9,
    "duration": 1.203
  },
  {
    "text": "- This is him with stubble. Hmm.",
    "start": 89.103,
    "duration": 2.697
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Roger can grow\nbetter beard than you.",
    "start": 91.8,
    "duration": 2.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 94.5,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "- Unique and awesome ingredients here.",
    "start": 95.67,
    "duration": 2.163
  },
  {
    "text": "So the first things we're going to grab",
    "start": 98.93,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "is a bunch of pork bones and chicken bones",
    "start": 99.92,
    "duration": 1.89
  },
  {
    "text": "with that really flavorful stuff.",
    "start": 101.81,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "- Pork bone, chicken bone: correct.",
    "start": 103.45,
    "duration": 1.99
  },
  {
    "text": "But Nephew Nick, iron your shirt.",
    "start": 105.44,
    "duration": 2.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 107.61,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "What graduate can't afford iron?",
    "start": 109.77,
    "duration": 2.328
  },
  {
    "text": "- It was like negative 8\nmillion degrees in here.",
    "start": 112.098,
    "duration": 2.657
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm frigid.",
    "start": 114.755,
    "duration": 1.335
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh, you should join team Auntie Helen.",
    "start": 116.09,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "She frigid also.",
    "start": 118.17,
    "duration": 1.75
  },
  {
    "text": "- Well, we got the pork\nbelly, so let's get home",
    "start": 119.92,
    "duration": 2.23
  },
  {
    "text": "and make some ramen.",
    "start": 122.15,
    "duration": 0.94
  },
  {
    "text": "There's nothing like a\ngood Japanese eggplant.",
    "start": 123.09,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "Got to find a place to\nput this for the drive.",
    "start": 125.52,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ugh. Uncle Roger wish I didn't see that.",
    "start": 127.22,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Nephew Nick, apologize to the children.",
    "start": 130.58,
    "duration": 0.904
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 131.484,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- I'm going to start making\nthat amazing ramen broth.",
    "start": 133.546,
    "duration": 2.854
  },
  {
    "text": "First, I'm going to go in\nwith all my chicken wings.",
    "start": 136.4,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Next I'm going to start\ntaking these pork hocks",
    "start": 138.65,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "that we got from the Asian grocery -",
    "start": 140.69,
    "duration": 1.23
  },
  {
    "text": "- Pork hock?",
    "start": 141.92,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "- As you can see here,",
    "start": 142.96,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "there is some meat on the outsides there,",
    "start": 143.793,
    "duration": 1.702
  },
  {
    "text": "but you've got a nice big\nchunk of bone in there",
    "start": 145.495,
    "duration": 1.232
  },
  {
    "text": "with tons of flavor.",
    "start": 146.727,
    "duration": 1.473
  },
  {
    "text": "- No, no, no. Pork hock,\ntoo much meat on there.",
    "start": 148.2,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "You should be using pork\nbone, not pork hock.",
    "start": 152.16,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "If you make tonkotsu broth with hock,",
    "start": 155.16,
    "duration": 2.39
  },
  {
    "text": "you're going to have too much\nmeat falling off from broth.",
    "start": 157.55,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Make it dirty.",
    "start": 160.37,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "- Once I've tossed in\nall of those pork bones",
    "start": 162.08,
    "duration": 2.02
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to go ahead",
    "start": 164.1,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "and add my last bit of protein in there,",
    "start": 164.933,
    "duration": 1.347
  },
  {
    "text": "which are duck wings.",
    "start": 166.28,
    "duration": 1.07
  },
  {
    "text": "- Duck wing?",
    "start": 167.35,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Nobody use duck wing for tonkotsu.",
    "start": 168.32,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa...",
    "start": 172.0,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "We use pork bone and maybe chicken bone,",
    "start": 172.97,
    "duration": 3.16
  },
  {
    "text": "but I think Nephew Nick\nwant to kill all the animal.",
    "start": 176.13,
    "duration": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Why don't you put elephant\nwing in there also?",
    "start": 179.27,
    "duration": 2.53
  },
  {
    "text": "- I'm going to cover all of this up",
    "start": 181.8,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "with some nice cold and crisp water.",
    "start": 183.1,
    "duration": 2.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Then crank up the heat",
    "start": 185.13,
    "duration": 1.08
  },
  {
    "text": "and bring this to a nice rolling boil.",
    "start": 186.21,
    "duration": 1.73
  },
  {
    "text": "- Niece and nephew, screenshot this image,",
    "start": 187.94,
    "duration": 2.42
  },
  {
    "text": "and send to your weakest friend,",
    "start": 190.36,
    "duration": 1.923
  },
  {
    "text": "because this is weaken's worst nightmare.",
    "start": 193.294,
    "duration": 2.006
  },
  {
    "text": "They see that even dead animal\nhave more company than them.",
    "start": 195.3,
    "duration": 3.499
  },
  {
    "text": "(air horn blasting)",
    "start": 198.799,
    "duration": 1.234
  },
  {
    "text": "- Once this has come to a rolling boil,",
    "start": 200.033,
    "duration": 1.467
  },
  {
    "text": "clear off some of the scum",
    "start": 201.5,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "that begins to form on the top.",
    "start": 202.64,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Some people will tell you to\nrinse this all the way out",
    "start": 204.02,
    "duration": 2.05
  },
  {
    "text": "but I like to keep all\nthe flavor of this stone",
    "start": 206.07,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "there from the bone.",
    "start": 207.87,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "So I don't like to rinse it out.",
    "start": 208.703,
    "duration": 1.037
  },
  {
    "text": "- No, no, no.",
    "start": 209.74,
    "duration": 1.3
  },
  {
    "text": "You have to rinse out.",
    "start": 211.04,
    "duration": 2.23
  },
  {
    "text": "Otherwise your broth gonna be so dirty.",
    "start": 213.27,
    "duration": 2.73
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 216.0,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at your water.",
    "start": 217.18,
    "duration": 0.932
  },
  {
    "text": "Look at your water.",
    "start": 218.112,
    "duration": 1.428
  },
  {
    "text": "It's so pink already",
    "start": 219.54,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "because there's so much\nscum in animal bone.",
    "start": 221.08,
    "duration": 2.86
  },
  {
    "text": "It look bad, but it also taste weird.",
    "start": 223.94,
    "duration": 2.51
  },
  {
    "text": "You need to soak water overnight,",
    "start": 226.45,
    "duration": 2.15
  },
  {
    "text": "throw water away,",
    "start": 228.6,
    "duration": 1.29
  },
  {
    "text": "clean the bone,",
    "start": 229.89,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "and start over with fresh water.",
    "start": 230.94,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 233.42,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Roger predict Nephew Nick broth",
    "start": 234.56,
    "duration": 2.58
  },
  {
    "text": "gonna be so dirty.",
    "start": 237.14,
    "duration": 1.61
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see if I correct.",
    "start": 238.75,
    "duration": 1.58
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now is when we let this\ngo overnight for 12 hours.",
    "start": 240.33,
    "duration": 3.57
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay, 12 hour, okay.",
    "start": 243.9,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "- Next we'll do our chashu pork belly.",
    "start": 245.72,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Now this part you don't\nhave to do overnight",
    "start": 247.38,
    "duration": 1.68
  },
  {
    "text": "but I'm going to sous vide\nit to get it really soft.",
    "start": 249.06,
    "duration": 2.41
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ooh, he sous vide pork belly.",
    "start": 251.47,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "This nephew so fancy.",
    "start": 254.54,
    "duration": 1.836
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ Fancy ♪",
    "start": 256.376,
    "duration": 1.324
  },
  {
    "text": "- So I'm going to let\nthis go overnight as well.",
    "start": 257.7,
    "duration": 1.87
  },
  {
    "text": "This pork has been very bad,",
    "start": 259.57,
    "duration": 1.223
  },
  {
    "text": "(slaps pork)",
    "start": 260.793,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "so we have to tie it up. First -",
    "start": 261.626,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ugh.",
    "start": 263.419,
    "duration": 2.41
  },
  {
    "text": "(slaps pork)",
    "start": 265.829,
    "duration": 1.03
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ew.",
    "start": 266.859,
    "duration": 0.891
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't spank your dinner.",
    "start": 267.75,
    "duration": 2.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Get room and spank your girlfriend.",
    "start": 270.17,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Leave the poor pork alone.",
    "start": 272.61,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "- For our sous vide,",
    "start": 274.97,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "the first thing we'll do",
    "start": 275.803,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "is put this finally rolled up pork",
    "start": 276.636,
    "duration": 1.644
  },
  {
    "text": "into a nice large bag,",
    "start": 278.28,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "add four cloves of garlic",
    "start": 279.92,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "a few hunks of ginger,",
    "start": 281.34,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "green onion,",
    "start": 282.51,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "soy sauce.",
    "start": 283.343,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ingredient not bad. Okay.",
    "start": 284.176,
    "duration": 2.624
  },
  {
    "text": "- One third cup of this\nextremely pungent fish sauce.",
    "start": 286.8,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "- Fish sauce a bit weird.",
    "start": 289.8,
    "duration": 1.61
  },
  {
    "text": "- Sugar, about a half a cup or so.",
    "start": 291.41,
    "duration": 1.85
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, inside the bag,",
    "start": 293.26,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "we're going to massage\nthe heck out of our meat.",
    "start": 294.66,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "- Stop it.",
    "start": 298.47,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Stop it.",
    "start": 299.69,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 300.95,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you making cooking video,",
    "start": 302.09,
    "duration": 2.03
  },
  {
    "text": "or auditioning for Bang Bros?",
    "start": 304.12,
    "duration": 2.19
  },
  {
    "text": "I feel bad for this guy girlfriend now.",
    "start": 306.31,
    "duration": 2.54
  },
  {
    "text": "I think he will do to girlfriend",
    "start": 308.85,
    "duration": 2.14
  },
  {
    "text": "what he do to pork belly.",
    "start": 310.99,
    "duration": 1.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Spank her,",
    "start": 312.89,
    "duration": 0.96
  },
  {
    "text": "tie her up,",
    "start": 313.85,
    "duration": 0.91
  },
  {
    "text": "and dip her in fish sauce.",
    "start": 314.76,
    "duration": 1.917
  },
  {
    "text": "That actually sound quite nice.",
    "start": 316.677,
    "duration": 2.382
  },
  {
    "text": "(sexy music playing)",
    "start": 319.059,
    "duration": 1.981
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry, children.",
    "start": 321.04,
    "duration": 1.055
  },
  {
    "text": "(beep)",
    "start": 322.095,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now we're going to roll\nthis up extremely tight -",
    "start": 322.928,
    "duration": 1.122
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay. But at least he marinate the meat.",
    "start": 324.05,
    "duration": 2.51
  },
  {
    "text": "So not like Jamie Oliver.",
    "start": 326.56,
    "duration": 1.85
  },
  {
    "text": "White pork belly.",
    "start": 328.41,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "- And cook this overnight\nfor about 12 to 15 hours.",
    "start": 329.59,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay. It's the next morning.",
    "start": 333.01,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "I was tending to that ramen broth",
    "start": 334.27,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "throughout the night.",
    "start": 336.04,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh really?",
    "start": 336.873,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "I thought you will be spanking someone.",
    "start": 337.706,
    "duration": 2.384
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now, we blew the fuse\nthree times last night.",
    "start": 340.09,
    "duration": 2.41
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's start with our soft boiled eggs.",
    "start": 342.5,
    "duration": 1.57
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that our water is boiling,",
    "start": 344.07,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "we're ready to add those eggs.",
    "start": 345.17,
    "duration": 1.17
  },
  {
    "text": "But first we're going to add",
    "start": 346.34,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "about a tablespoon or two of vinegar",
    "start": 347.173,
    "duration": 1.897
  },
  {
    "text": "which is actually going to prevent",
    "start": 349.07,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "running of the whites -",
    "start": 350.06,
    "duration": 1.31
  },
  {
    "text": "- Runnning of the whites.",
    "start": 351.37,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "That what Uncle Roger\ncall every marathon ever.",
    "start": 352.79,
    "duration": 3.1
  },
  {
    "text": "- I'll drop in my six eggs,",
    "start": 355.89,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "place on the lid.",
    "start": 356.93,
    "duration": 1.1
  },
  {
    "text": "But we're going to do it",
    "start": 358.03,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "for six minutes and nine seconds,",
    "start": 358.863,
    "duration": 1.477
  },
  {
    "text": "which I promise you,",
    "start": 360.34,
    "duration": 0.849
  },
  {
    "text": "(record scratch)",
    "start": 361.189,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "it sounds silly,",
    "start": 362.022,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "but it's the perfect time",
    "start": 362.855,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "for a soft boiled egg.",
    "start": 363.688,
    "duration": 1.022
  },
  {
    "text": "- Six minute nine seconds.",
    "start": 364.71,
    "duration": 2.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 366.99,
    "duration": 1.047
  },
  {
    "text": "Another dirty joke by this guy.",
    "start": 368.037,
    "duration": 3.063
  },
  {
    "text": "I can't believe this guy video.",
    "start": 371.1,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Dirtier than my Nigella Lawson video.",
    "start": 373.42,
    "duration": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "- Here I have a really cold ice bath.",
    "start": 376.56,
    "duration": 1.82
  },
  {
    "text": "- Good, good.",
    "start": 378.38,
    "duration": 0.89
  },
  {
    "text": "Good technique.",
    "start": 379.27,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Straight into the ice\nbath to halt their cooking.",
    "start": 380.103,
    "duration": 1.927
  },
  {
    "text": "For our ramen egg marinade,",
    "start": 382.03,
    "duration": 1.27
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll combine three quarters cup of mirin,",
    "start": 383.3,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "quarter cup soy sauce.",
    "start": 385.3,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Good.",
    "start": 386.133,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Dark soy sauce.",
    "start": 386.966,
    "duration": 0.904
  },
  {
    "text": "If you can't find dark soy sauce -",
    "start": 387.87,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ingredient all correct.",
    "start": 388.703,
    "duration": 1.337
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now it's time to peel our eggs,",
    "start": 390.04,
    "duration": 1.51
  },
  {
    "text": "but I just wanted to show you guys first,",
    "start": 391.55,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "how perfect that yoke on the inside is.",
    "start": 393.32,
    "duration": 1.804
  },
  {
    "text": "- Mm.",
    "start": 395.124,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- I told you it's amazing",
    "start": 395.957,
    "duration": 1.813
  },
  {
    "text": "- Uncle Roger feel like I need shower",
    "start": 397.77,
    "duration": 2.24
  },
  {
    "text": "after watching this video.",
    "start": 400.01,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "- Drop them right in that soy bath.",
    "start": 401.79,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll cover these with plastic wrap",
    "start": 403.27,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "and allow them to soak for several hours.",
    "start": 404.87,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ah! Niece and nephew.",
    "start": 406.51,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You see this.",
    "start": 407.89,
    "duration": 0.95
  },
  {
    "text": "If you use plastic wrap like this,",
    "start": 408.84,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "the top of it won't be marinated",
    "start": 410.82,
    "duration": 2.47
  },
  {
    "text": "because it touching plastic,",
    "start": 413.29,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "not the liquid.",
    "start": 415.0,
    "duration": 0.9
  },
  {
    "text": "It will have one white spot on it.",
    "start": 415.9,
    "duration": 2.13
  },
  {
    "text": "Pro tip: Use paper towel.",
    "start": 418.03,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Like how Way of Ramen channel do with egg.",
    "start": 420.28,
    "duration": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "- Our eggs are all set.",
    "start": 423.42,
    "duration": 1.27
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, we're going to make our tare.",
    "start": 424.69,
    "duration": 0.89
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ah! He making tare.",
    "start": 425.58,
    "duration": 2.87
  },
  {
    "text": "This already better than\nJamie and Nigella ramen.",
    "start": 428.45,
    "duration": 3.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Tare is the soul of ramen.",
    "start": 431.93,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "It the flavoring for the broth.",
    "start": 434.18,
    "duration": 2.15
  },
  {
    "text": "- First, we're going to\nstart with our dashi.",
    "start": 436.33,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Add about three and a half\nto four cups of water,",
    "start": 438.17,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "three sheets of kombu",
    "start": 440.01,
    "duration": 1.49
  },
  {
    "text": "and really let this heat up,",
    "start": 441.5,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "but we don't want to boil it.",
    "start": 442.333,
    "duration": 1.385
  },
  {
    "text": "- Correct. Don't boil kombu.",
    "start": 443.718,
    "duration": 2.162
  },
  {
    "text": "- Basically, dashi is this",
    "start": 445.88,
    "duration": 1.03
  },
  {
    "text": "umami-packed Japanese soup stock.",
    "start": 446.91,
    "duration": 2.35
  },
  {
    "text": "It's used in so many different things.",
    "start": 449.26,
    "duration": 1.85
  },
  {
    "text": "And this is how we're going\nto build the foundation.",
    "start": 451.11,
    "duration": 2.09
  },
  {
    "text": "- This guy really loves shot of his hand.",
    "start": 453.2,
    "duration": 2.47
  },
  {
    "text": "So many close up of his hand.",
    "start": 455.67,
    "duration": 2.15
  },
  {
    "text": "Is he hand model or something?",
    "start": 457.82,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Imagine if Uncle Roger make cooking video.",
    "start": 459.52,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "And all you see is:",
    "start": 462.64,
    "duration": 1.413
  },
  {
    "text": "- Cup of bonito flakes.",
    "start": 466.54,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay.",
    "start": 467.75,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Dried shiitaki mushrooms.",
    "start": 468.583,
    "duration": 1.127
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll turn off the heat and set it aside.",
    "start": 469.71,
    "duration": 1.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Once that incredible dashi is done,",
    "start": 471.69,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll strain it into a nice large -",
    "start": 473.49,
    "duration": 1.61
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh, pot too fast.",
    "start": 475.1,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Some liquid fell out.",
    "start": 476.14,
    "duration": 1.39
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't waste food.",
    "start": 477.53,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "- We're now keeping about\ntwo cups of our dashi.",
    "start": 478.58,
    "duration": 2.03
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll create our tare by\nadding one cup of soy.",
    "start": 480.61,
    "duration": 2.43
  },
  {
    "text": "- Oh good.",
    "start": 483.04,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "- This tare look like\nit got so much umami.",
    "start": 484.01,
    "duration": 2.77
  },
  {
    "text": "So no need MSG.",
    "start": 486.78,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "- Six cloves of garlic.",
    "start": 488.3,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "And then about two tablespoons\nof black peppercorns.",
    "start": 489.35,
    "duration": 2.33
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay. Tare not bad.",
    "start": 491.68,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now for our ramen.",
    "start": 493.92,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "Please do not use dry\ninstant ramen noodles.",
    "start": 495.13,
    "duration": 3.05
  },
  {
    "text": "This is an absolute no-go.",
    "start": 498.18,
    "duration": 1.913
  },
  {
    "text": "(bomb exploding)",
    "start": 500.093,
    "duration": 1.707
  },
  {
    "text": "- Correct.",
    "start": 501.8,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't use packet instant ramen",
    "start": 502.633,
    "duration": 1.927
  },
  {
    "text": "and also don't use soba like Jamie Oliver.",
    "start": 504.56,
    "duration": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "But Uncle Roger don't recommend",
    "start": 507.7,
    "duration": 2.11
  },
  {
    "text": "niece and nephew make ramen at home.",
    "start": 509.81,
    "duration": 1.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Tonkotsu ramen noodle,",
    "start": 511.75,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "very hard to get right at home.",
    "start": 513.53,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Just buy it from store.",
    "start": 515.13,
    "duration": 1.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Support your local Japanese store.",
    "start": 516.35,
    "duration": 2.37
  },
  {
    "text": "- Ramen noodles are very different,",
    "start": 518.72,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "in that they need to be alkalinated.",
    "start": 520.32,
    "duration": 1.78
  },
  {
    "text": "- Correct.",
    "start": 522.1,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- This is just a fancy way of saying",
    "start": 522.933,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "that we put baking soda in the dough.",
    "start": 523.766,
    "duration": 1.476
  },
  {
    "text": "- Small correction:",
    "start": 525.242,
    "duration": 2.058
  },
  {
    "text": "Baking soda is sodium bicarbonate.",
    "start": 527.3,
    "duration": 2.62
  },
  {
    "text": "But ramen, you need sodium carbonate.",
    "start": 529.92,
    "duration": 2.247
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Roger,",
    "start": 532.167,
    "duration": 1.633
  },
  {
    "text": "so chemistry.",
    "start": 533.8,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "- Switch on that spaghetti head,",
    "start": 535.15,
    "duration": 1.59
  },
  {
    "text": "and then you're ready to roll.",
    "start": 536.74,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "- I have to say it look pretty good.",
    "start": 539.53,
    "duration": 1.87
  },
  {
    "text": "- These look absolutely fantastic.",
    "start": 541.4,
    "duration": 2.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Cut it with a nice spray of bread flour.",
    "start": 543.78,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Just so nothing sticks.",
    "start": 545.62,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, our ramen is ready to be cooked.",
    "start": 546.98,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Right here is our 20 -",
    "start": 548.94,
    "duration": 1.061
  },
  {
    "text": "- What?",
    "start": 550.001,
    "duration": 1.242
  },
  {
    "text": "(soup glopping)",
    "start": 551.243,
    "duration": 2.729
  },
  {
    "text": "What?",
    "start": 553.972,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "That is disgusting.",
    "start": 554.805,
    "duration": 3.225
  },
  {
    "text": "Why this ramen broth look like this?",
    "start": 558.03,
    "duration": 3.333
  },
  {
    "text": "This look like roadkill.",
    "start": 561.363,
    "duration": 2.454
  },
  {
    "text": "Tonkotsu broth",
    "start": 563.817,
    "duration": 1.193
  },
  {
    "text": "not supposed to look like dirt water.",
    "start": 565.01,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 567.47,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "This what it supposed to look like.",
    "start": 568.71,
    "duration": 2.01
  },
  {
    "text": "If your ramen broth look like mud,",
    "start": 570.72,
    "duration": 2.17
  },
  {
    "text": "you fucked up.",
    "start": 572.89,
    "duration": 0.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Roger right.",
    "start": 573.73,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "I predicted earlier, his\nramen broth gonna be so dirty.",
    "start": 574.97,
    "duration": 4.07
  },
  {
    "text": "He didn't wash his bone.",
    "start": 579.04,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "He didn't throw out water,",
    "start": 580.52,
    "duration": 1.73
  },
  {
    "text": "and his bone have too much meat on there.",
    "start": 582.25,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "This broth as dirty as Nephew Nick brain.",
    "start": 584.65,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "- Gotta find a place to\nput this for the drive.",
    "start": 587.71,
    "duration": 1.65
  },
  {
    "text": "This pork has been very bad.",
    "start": 589.36,
    "duration": 1.35
  },
  {
    "text": "(slaps pork)",
    "start": 590.71,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Six minutes and nine seconds",
    "start": 591.543,
    "duration": 1.157
  },
  {
    "text": "- This broth messier than Auntie Helen.",
    "start": 592.7,
    "duration": 2.443
  },
  {
    "text": "- We're going to strain off all this broth",
    "start": 596.61,
    "duration": 1.75
  },
  {
    "text": "to make it nice and sweet.",
    "start": 598.36,
    "duration": 1.14
  },
  {
    "text": "- Even if you strain,",
    "start": 599.5,
    "duration": 1.27
  },
  {
    "text": "you can't strain out the brown color.",
    "start": 600.77,
    "duration": 3.022
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa...",
    "start": 603.792,
    "duration": 1.538
  },
  {
    "text": "- Next, we have our chashu,",
    "start": 605.33,
    "duration": 1.27
  },
  {
    "text": "which is our Japanese pork belly.",
    "start": 606.6,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "What you're looking at here is pork belly",
    "start": 608.34,
    "duration": 1.86
  },
  {
    "text": "that's cooked the entire night,",
    "start": 610.2,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "but I just can't help it.",
    "start": 611.84,
    "duration": 1.12
  },
  {
    "text": "I have to spank it.",
    "start": 612.96,
    "duration": 0.879
  },
  {
    "text": "(slaps pork)",
    "start": 613.839,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, though, I do want you",
    "start": 614.672,
    "duration": 1.268
  },
  {
    "text": "to look at the meat on the sides there.",
    "start": 615.94,
    "duration": 1.59
  },
  {
    "text": "Soft, perfectly tender, pulled pork.",
    "start": 617.53,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Pork belly,",
    "start": 619.99,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "it's been a pleasure getting to know you",
    "start": 620.823,
    "duration": 1.317
  },
  {
    "text": "these last 24 hours,",
    "start": 622.14,
    "duration": 1.27
  },
  {
    "text": "but now it's time to cut them.",
    "start": 623.41,
    "duration": 1.69
  },
  {
    "text": "- No, no, no, no, no, no, no.",
    "start": 625.1,
    "duration": 2.83
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't cut pork belly when it hot.",
    "start": 627.93,
    "duration": 3.267
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 631.197,
    "duration": 1.223
  },
  {
    "text": "It not solid enough.",
    "start": 632.42,
    "duration": 1.75
  },
  {
    "text": "You have to take pork belly out,",
    "start": 634.17,
    "duration": 2.1
  },
  {
    "text": "chill it overnight,",
    "start": 636.27,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "and then cut it when it colder.",
    "start": 637.71,
    "duration": 2.657
  },
  {
    "text": "Ugh.",
    "start": 640.367,
    "duration": 1.793
  },
  {
    "text": "First you spank pork belly",
    "start": 642.16,
    "duration": 2.22
  },
  {
    "text": "and then you cut it when it warm.",
    "start": 644.38,
    "duration": 2.05
  },
  {
    "text": "What has pork belly done to deserve this?",
    "start": 646.43,
    "duration": 2.69
  },
  {
    "text": "I have to put my leg\ndown from chair again.",
    "start": 649.12,
    "duration": 2.73
  },
  {
    "text": "It gonna go all over the place.",
    "start": 651.85,
    "duration": 2.65
  },
  {
    "text": "- So let's get a couple of\nnice slices just right through.",
    "start": 654.5,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "- See?",
    "start": 657.07,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- You know, it's funny.",
    "start": 657.903,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "It's almost so soft and tender",
    "start": 658.736,
    "duration": 1.494
  },
  {
    "text": "that I can't really get any slices.",
    "start": 660.23,
    "duration": 1.708
  },
  {
    "text": "- What I tell you?",
    "start": 661.938,
    "duration": 1.804
  },
  {
    "text": "What I tell you?",
    "start": 663.742,
    "duration": 1.138
  },
  {
    "text": "- So that's good enough for me.",
    "start": 664.88,
    "duration": 1.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Once I've pulled off\nthe pork belly's thong,",
    "start": 666.13,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I can get a few more -",
    "start": 668.13,
    "duration": 0.937
  },
  {
    "text": "- See, if you chop like this...",
    "start": 669.067,
    "duration": 2.393
  },
  {
    "text": "- Too tender to do what we're looking for.",
    "start": 671.46,
    "duration": 1.477
  },
  {
    "text": "- You just making pulled pork now.",
    "start": 672.937,
    "duration": 2.423
  },
  {
    "text": "That's not chashu.",
    "start": 675.36,
    "duration": 1.555
  },
  {
    "text": "(sighs)",
    "start": 676.915,
    "duration": 0.885
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now it's time to finally\nopen up those soft boiled eggs.",
    "start": 677.8,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": "First let's cross our fingers",
    "start": 680.77,
    "duration": 1.37
  },
  {
    "text": "that we got that color from those eggs.",
    "start": 682.14,
    "duration": 1.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Just to show you a little\nspot on the top of the egg",
    "start": 683.84,
    "duration": 2.29
  },
  {
    "text": "that was not submerged.",
    "start": 686.13,
    "duration": 1.32
  },
  {
    "text": "- See? Uncle Roger predicted this also.",
    "start": 687.45,
    "duration": 3.03
  },
  {
    "text": "- We're going to cut through that egg",
    "start": 690.48,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "very clean and keeping\nall that yolk inside.",
    "start": 691.92,
    "duration": 2.42
  },
  {
    "text": "- Texture good.",
    "start": 694.34,
    "duration": 0.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Texture very good.",
    "start": 695.33,
    "duration": 1.04
  },
  {
    "text": "- I've clearly gotten some of that soy.",
    "start": 696.37,
    "duration": 1.69
  },
  {
    "text": "- Maybe you can submerge a bit more time",
    "start": 698.06,
    "duration": 2.47
  },
  {
    "text": "because you see it brown on\noutside, white on inside,",
    "start": 700.53,
    "duration": 3.56
  },
  {
    "text": "just like Auntie Hersha.",
    "start": 704.09,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "- And boy, oh boy.",
    "start": 705.51,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "Aren't those yolks incredible.",
    "start": 706.56,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Just look at how soft and amazing it is.",
    "start": 707.98,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "Now we've reached the final\nshot, where we assemble.",
    "start": 710.05,
    "duration": 2.57
  },
  {
    "text": "I know this is the moment\nyou've all been waiting for.",
    "start": 712.62,
    "duration": 2.127
  },
  {
    "text": "- His hand again.",
    "start": 714.747,
    "duration": 1.353
  },
  {
    "text": "- After mixing it around a little bit,",
    "start": 716.1,
    "duration": 1.51
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll place in a nice\nspoonful or two of my tare.",
    "start": 717.61,
    "duration": 2.593
  },
  {
    "text": "- Tare go in.",
    "start": 720.203,
    "duration": 0.967
  },
  {
    "text": "- Then comes my actual broth.",
    "start": 721.17,
    "duration": 1.497
  },
  {
    "text": "- (sighs)",
    "start": 722.667,
    "duration": 1.563
  },
  {
    "text": "Is dirty broth.",
    "start": 724.23,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "- So it's amazing",
    "start": 725.47,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "to finally be able to\nput it into the bowl.",
    "start": 726.303,
    "duration": 1.667
  },
  {
    "text": "Where are the actual ramen noodles?",
    "start": 727.97,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Those should be placed",
    "start": 729.68,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "into this hot broth",
    "start": 730.56,
    "duration": 1.05
  },
  {
    "text": "immediately when they finish.",
    "start": 731.61,
    "duration": 1.944
  },
  {
    "text": "- Wait.",
    "start": 733.554,
    "duration": 0.966
  },
  {
    "text": "- Those should be placed into\nthis hot broth immediately.",
    "start": 734.52,
    "duration": 2.75
  },
  {
    "text": "- You say it should be placed immediately,",
    "start": 737.27,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "but then you hadn't even prepared ramen",
    "start": 740.63,
    "duration": 3.47
  },
  {
    "text": "to go in.",
    "start": 744.1,
    "duration": 1.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Does the word \"immediately\"",
    "start": 745.91,
    "duration": 1.61
  },
  {
    "text": "mean something different to you?",
    "start": 747.52,
    "duration": 2.29
  },
  {
    "text": "You should cook the ramen beforehand",
    "start": 749.81,
    "duration": 2.33
  },
  {
    "text": "and everything go in at the same time.",
    "start": 752.14,
    "duration": 3.17
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't cook ramen after you start plating,",
    "start": 755.31,
    "duration": 3.02
  },
  {
    "text": "because when you cooking ramen,",
    "start": 758.33,
    "duration": 1.77
  },
  {
    "text": "the broth gonna get cold.",
    "start": 760.1,
    "duration": 1.615
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa.",
    "start": 761.715,
    "duration": 1.175
  },
  {
    "text": "- And once it's boiling\nover very high heat,",
    "start": 762.89,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll toss in our ramen noodles.",
    "start": 764.93,
    "duration": 1.18
  },
  {
    "text": "And then for just a minute\nand 30 seconds or so",
    "start": 766.11,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "we'll let this cook.",
    "start": 768.55,
    "duration": 0.97
  },
  {
    "text": "Admire how amazing -",
    "start": 769.52,
    "duration": 1.26
  },
  {
    "text": "- Mm, look a bit soft.",
    "start": 770.78,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "- After one or two shakes,",
    "start": 772.26,
    "duration": 1.114
  },
  {
    "text": "put it directly into my ramen broth.",
    "start": 773.374,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "And now we're ready\nfor that final plating.",
    "start": 775.71,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "So in go our -",
    "start": 777.43,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- That so much -",
    "start": 778.263,
    "duration": 0.941
  },
  {
    "text": "Wait.",
    "start": 779.204,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "That so much enoki.",
    "start": 780.037,
    "duration": 1.573
  },
  {
    "text": "It feels like you having\nenoki with side of ramen",
    "start": 781.61,
    "duration": 3.93
  },
  {
    "text": "- Then we'll go right in the middle",
    "start": 785.54,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "with those gorgeous eggs.",
    "start": 786.7,
    "duration": 1.45
  },
  {
    "text": "Then we have our beautiful pork.",
    "start": 788.15,
    "duration": 1.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Then a nice, generous\nhandful of green onions",
    "start": 789.65,
    "duration": 2.33
  },
  {
    "text": "and last but not least, some nori",
    "start": 791.98,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "that I've actually gotten -",
    "start": 793.7,
    "duration": 0.847
  },
  {
    "text": "- Nori weird shape.",
    "start": 794.547,
    "duration": 2.003
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now, there is one of the\nmost gorgeous ramen bowls",
    "start": 796.55,
    "duration": 1.588
  },
  {
    "text": "I've ever seen.",
    "start": 798.138,
    "duration": 1.282
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, before we eat this,",
    "start": 799.42,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to paint the pork\nin a little bit more fat.",
    "start": 800.58,
    "duration": 2.194
  },
  {
    "text": "- Okay. That fancy.",
    "start": 802.774,
    "duration": 1.656
  },
  {
    "text": "Torching.",
    "start": 804.43,
    "duration": 0.88
  },
  {
    "text": "Haiyaa, but torching good,",
    "start": 805.31,
    "duration": 2.33
  },
  {
    "text": "but don't torch your pork next to the egg.",
    "start": 807.64,
    "duration": 3.067
  },
  {
    "text": "You gonna cook the egg by accident.",
    "start": 810.707,
    "duration": 2.103
  },
  {
    "text": "Torch it elsewhere.",
    "start": 812.81,
    "duration": 0.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Your house so big.",
    "start": 813.68,
    "duration": 1.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Go find some other room\nto torch your pork.",
    "start": 814.71,
    "duration": 2.378
  },
  {
    "text": "(torch sizzling)",
    "start": 817.088,
    "duration": 1.532
  },
  {
    "text": "- Now our ramen is ready to eat.",
    "start": 818.62,
    "duration": 1.74
  },
  {
    "text": "I do want to say",
    "start": 820.36,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "that this is one of the most\nbeautiful bowls of ramen",
    "start": 821.193,
    "duration": 1.871
  },
  {
    "text": "I've ever seen.",
    "start": 823.064,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Hmm! Okay.",
    "start": 823.897,
    "duration": 1.493
  },
  {
    "text": "This ramen better than\nNigella and Jamie ramen",
    "start": 825.39,
    "duration": 3.14
  },
  {
    "text": "because he actually make tare.",
    "start": 828.53,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "But Nephew Nick, tonkotsu\nsupposed to be white,",
    "start": 830.69,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "creamy and sexy,",
    "start": 833.69,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": "not like brown water.",
    "start": 835.16,
    "duration": 1.31
  },
  {
    "text": "That the biggest mistake he made,",
    "start": 836.47,
    "duration": 2.09
  },
  {
    "text": "but Uncle Roger like how\nmuch effort he put in.",
    "start": 838.56,
    "duration": 2.91
  },
  {
    "text": "He making noodle from scratch.",
    "start": 841.47,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "That not easy.",
    "start": 843.83,
    "duration": 1.03
  },
  {
    "text": "Out of five component of ramen,",
    "start": 844.86,
    "duration": 2.36
  },
  {
    "text": "I think he have at least four.",
    "start": 847.22,
    "duration": 2.13
  },
  {
    "text": "He forgot to make aroma oil.",
    "start": 849.35,
    "duration": 2.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Nephew Nick, next time\nclean your pork bone.",
    "start": 851.69,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't cut pork belly when it hot.",
    "start": 854.33,
    "duration": 2.07
  },
  {
    "text": "And no more spanking in cooking video.",
    "start": 856.4,
    "duration": 3.25
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Rogers so glad I picked\nwearing my orange polo,",
    "start": 859.65,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "not tank top,",
    "start": 863.81,
    "duration": 1.02
  },
  {
    "text": "because niece and nephew get so thirsty.",
    "start": 864.83,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe next video,",
    "start": 867.83,
    "duration": 1.21
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Roger will read\nall the best comments",
    "start": 869.04,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "left by niece and nephew.",
    "start": 872.12,
    "duration": 1.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me know if I should do it.",
    "start": 873.5,
    "duration": 1.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Comment down below.",
    "start": 874.96,
    "duration": 1.098
  },
  {
    "text": "(beep)",
    "start": 876.058,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "This guy Harvard graduate,\nMaster Chef finalist",
    "start": 876.891,
    "duration": 3.469
  },
  {
    "text": "and have smoothest baby face in whole -",
    "start": 880.36,
    "duration": 2.696
  },
  {
    "text": "(laughs)",
    "start": 883.056,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "(clears throat)",
    "start": 884.992,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "(beep)",
    "start": 885.825,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Get a room and spank girlfriend instead,",
    "start": 886.658,
    "duration": 3.172
  },
  {
    "text": "leave pork alone.",
    "start": 889.83,
    "duration": 1.66
  },
  {
    "text": "Pork didn't do shit.",
    "start": 891.49,
    "duration": 2.229
  },
  {
    "text": "(laughs)",
    "start": 893.719,
    "duration": 1.991
  },
  {
    "text": "- Sorry, Nick's girlfriend.",
    "start": 895.71,
    "duration": 1.599
  },
  {
    "text": "(beep)",
    "start": 897.309,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "- Are you making cooking video",
    "start": 898.142,
    "duration": 1.698
  },
  {
    "text": "or auditioning for Bang Bros?",
    "start": 899.84,
    "duration": 2.551
  },
  {
    "text": "(laughs)",
    "start": 902.391,
    "duration": 2.504
  },
  {
    "text": "(beep)",
    "start": 904.895,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Running of the whites.",
    "start": 905.728,
    "duration": 0.962
  },
  {
    "text": "That what I call every Black Friday sale.",
    "start": 906.69,
    "duration": 2.656
  },
  {
    "text": "(beep)",
    "start": 909.346,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Nephew Nick, next time clean your bone.",
    "start": 910.179,
    "duration": 1.981
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't -",
    "start": 912.16,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "No, that sounds dirty.",
    "start": 912.993,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Not like that.",
    "start": 915.233,
    "duration": 0.927
  },
  {
    "text": "Uncle Roger don't mean dirty like that.",
    "start": 916.16,
    "duration": 2.262
  },
  {
    "text": "(beep)",
    "start": 918.422,
    "duration": 0.833
  },
  {
    "text": "Niece and nephew, remember",
    "start": 919.255,
    "duration": 1.195
  },
  {
    "text": "to go watch Nephew Nigel podcast clip",
    "start": 920.45,
    "duration": 2.71
  },
  {
    "text": "about Italian Uncle Roger.",
    "start": 923.16,
    "duration": 2.09
  },
  {
    "text": "Go, go click on that.",
    "start": 925.25,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "Click on that.",
    "start": 927.45,
    "duration": 1.635
  },
  {
    "text": "(jazz music playing)",
    "start": 929.085,
    "duration": 3.083
  }
]